{"tid":412111,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆外遇點算好","createTime":"2017-09-24T11:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T12:55:24.000Z","uid":135701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"235aca174e9ca35bece8e38a3518dbc33712e0e2","tid":412111,"uid":135701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"我朋友發現佢老豆有外遇，外遇對像係一個後生女，但係佢老豆係人前都表現到好愛佢老婆咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實上佢老母係婚姻關係上表現得橫行霸道，令佢老豆同我朋友都覺得佢好衰。<br />\n不過根據朋友講法，佢老母最近都變左，對人溫柔返，但係佢老豆就正正係呢段應該會更恩愛嘅時期搵左個小三。<br />\n我朋友宜家扮緊唔知老豆有外遇，驚同老母講會傷佢老母心，又驚同老豆講佢老豆會反面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望各位巴絲可以幫幫忙，諗下呢個情况下我朋友可以做啲乜。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64c53253bfb271b7b756033c11ec032087212bb","tid":412111,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"其實你老母已經sense到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190ffc043408ee4098574343fda749c3ad8f73fd","tid":412111,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"爆佢大鑊<br />\n伸張正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9717ddb99b3bbbc7ffbba31f3e7a65f77e090d09","tid":412111,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"有咩所謂，反正你朋友唔係佢老豆親生"},{"pid":"227ed31b2618e4e4a8929c3145a450dc96e4695d","tid":412111,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5348c757545296048e473f18712d5524dfb1d893","tid":412111,"uid":34075,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:29:17.000Z","msg":"小你老母三"},{"pid":"dd53e21e73e4c23574de4ff660edafbea08d415e","tid":412111,"uid":90978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201